00:45:13.840 --> 00:45:20.190
Young age -- Alberto is only
17, and love for poetry.

00:45:20.190 --> 00:45:24.880
One of the nine had already
published a book of poetry.

00:45:24.880 --> 00:45:29.550
The youngest was 17 and the
oldest was 21 years old.

00:45:29.550 --> 00:45:39.630
So in this way, the story of
Alice and Sarah intersects

00:45:39.630 --> 00:45:44.400
